<br>
Instant Army is a raiding group composed of people who for their own various reasons choose to work together as a group.  Although a lot of people get their epics while being in this group, it is not designed for people to come and get help for their epics. (We have met Kamie, and I doubt this is your sole intent, just want to be sure it is clear for others reading this...if somebody is looking to get their epic, this is a long, hard, way to do it...not a quick route).  <br>
<br>
If your focus is on being a 24/7 raider, it is probably not the place for you.  There are many excellent raiding guilds in Firiona Vie who would probably be a better choice.  We are basically a group who has fun raiding together (although we are serious about doing it, doing it well, and striving to take on bigger and bigger challenges as time goes on).<br>
<br>
Membership is based on invitation by a sponsor who is already in the group and raiding for a while until the group is sufficiently comfortable that you will fit in with the group and add value as a member.<br>
<br>
